com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.documents

Interface ExportableDocument

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultPhylogenyDocument, DefaultSameTaxaTreesDocument, DefaultTreeDocument

    public interface ExportableDocument
    Interface implemented by plugin documents that wish to implemenet a specialized export.

    Geneious provides a default export for standard document types (Sequences, Trees, etc) when appropriate.
